{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idefaa3a94-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s3321"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3321"},"text":"§ 3321.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Statement of purpose","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"It is the purpose of this subchapter to promote research and extension activities of the institutions hereinafter referred to in ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t7/s3322/b"},"text":"section 3322(b) of this title","children":[],"tail":", and to coordinate their efforts as an integral part in the implementation of the National Aquaculture Act of 1980 ("},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t16/s2801"},"text":"16 U.S.C. 2801","children":[],"tail":" et seq.) by encouraging landowners, individuals, and commercial institutions to develop aquaculture production and facilities and sound aquacultural practices that will, through research and technology transfer programs, provide for the increased production and marketing of aquacultural food products."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idefaa3a95-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/95/113/tXIV/s1474"},"text":"Pub. L. 95–113, title XIV, § 1474","children":[],"tail":", as added "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/97/98/tXIV/s1440/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 97–98, title XIV, § 1440(a)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1981-12-22"},"text":"Dec. 22, 1981","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/95/1316"},"text":"95 Stat. 1316","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idefaa3a96-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"idefaa3a97-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"idefaa3a98-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The National Aquaculture Act of 1980, referred to in text, is ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/96/362"},"text":"Pub. L. 96–362","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1980-09-26"},"text":"Sept. 26, 1980","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/94/1198"},"text":"94 Stat. 1198","children":[],"tail":", which is classified generally to chapter 48 (§ 2801 et seq.) of Title 16, Conservation. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Short Title note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t16/s2801"},"text":"section 2801 of Title 16","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"statutoryNotes","id":"idefaa3a99-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"effectiveDate","id":"idefaa3a9a-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Effective Date","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section effective ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1981-12-22"},"text":"Dec. 22, 1981","children":[],"tail":", see "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/97/98/s1801"},"text":"section 1801 of Pub. L. 97–98","children":[],"tail":", set out as a note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t7/s4301"},"text":"se